    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Welcome aboard\nBOAC\nThis issue is\na Christmas present",
      "Tommy Steele, who has been looking\nforward to playing Santa Claus for years,\nis on the front cover with some of the\ngifts he's chosen.\nInside we give you a traditional\nChristmas dinner, a ticket for the panto-\nmime, a new Cbristmas game, atripto\nthe Caribbean in search of pirates and a\ndetective story.\nYou don't have towait till December\n25th to read it."
